fivenodes <- data.frame(rbind(
    df %>% filter(dataset=='fivenodes' & mtype=='rand' & inter_method == 'linear' & nof_filters==12 & lags==2 & epoch==50 & model=='GConvLSTM' & 
                  ( mrate == 0.3  | mrate == 0.5  |mrate ==  0.6 | mrate == 0.7  | mrate ==  0.8)),

                  ( mrate == 0.3  | mrate == 0.5  |mrate ==  0.6 | mrate == 0.7  | mrate ==  0.8)),

                  ( mrate == 0.3  | mrate == 0.5  |mrate ==  0.6 | mrate == 0.7  | mrate ==  0.8)),
